  m_Text: 'Tap START GAME to enter the barangay.


    Use the joystick to move.

    Tap
    the action button to talk to NPCs, accept quests, and begin cultural mini-games.


    Complete
    quests and quizzes to learn about pre-colonial Philippine life.'
